Charged Ex-Credit Suisse Banker Works in Switzerland, LZ Says

-- B y   L e i g h   B a l d w i n
-- 
2011-02-25T06:45:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-25/charged-ex-credit-suisse-banker-works-in-switzerland-lz-says.html
One of the former employees of  Credit Suisse Group AG  charged with aiding  tax evasion  in the
U.S. is working for Zuger Kantonalbank AG, Luzerner Zeitung
reported.  The banker joined Zuger Kantonalbank six months ago as an
adviser to private clients and has been on leave since yesterday
as the bank “clarifies the situation,” the Swiss paper
reported, citing an interview with the bank’s Chief Executive
Officer Pascal Niquille.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Leigh Baldwin in Zurich at 
 lbaldwin3@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at   acullen8@bloomberg.net . 